sourcesContent: function r(e){var t,f,n="";if("string"==typeof e||"number"==typeof e)n+=e;else if("object"==typeof e)if(Array.isArray(e))for(t=0;t<e.length;t++)e[t]&&(f=r(e[t]))&&(n&&(n+=" "),n+=f);else for(t in e)e[t]&&(n&&(n+=" "),n+=t);return n}export function clsx(){for(var e,t,f=0,n="";f<arguments.length;)(e=arguments[f++])&&(t=r(e))&&(n&&(n+=" "),n+=t);return n}export default clsx;
